title: The S&P's New High:  Too Late to Buy?
description: The S&P 500 hits a new high.  Trip Advisor soars.  Whole Foods delivers. And Amerian Express declines.  Our analysts discuss those stories and share some stocks on their radar.  Plus, corporate governance expert and film critic Nell Minow talks proxy voting, executive pay, and Academy Awards.
